node.text:
I think she has this whole going into the weekend thing handled…

I’m just grateful to follow with her stroller in case she gets tired and dance in her shadow.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jessica Capshaw on June 21, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Happiest of Birthdays to this ray of sunshine!! The sun always shines brighter when you are around…there’s no one with more sparkle in their eye or joy in their smile. Poppy, I am grateful every day that I get to be your Mom. Love you, sweet (and spicy) girl of love!!

node.text: My girls are horse 🐎 lovers through and through. #ad We are huge fans of @DreamWorksSpirit and are so excited to watch the next film in the series, #SpiritUntamed, which hits the theatres on June 4th. If your girls love horses as much as mine, you can watch the trailer now online for a preview of all the fun! Josie and I could play forever with Lucky’s train home play set while watching this trailer!! Check it out here and share your family’s favorite parts https://bit.ly/3uDOhdL @Mattel

node.text: I miss the sun kissed freckle days ♥️...#tbt

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jessica Capshaw on May 09, 2021 tagging @gap. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: Happy Mother’s Day to all the Lionesses and Mama Bears!! I couldn’t be more grateful to have been raised by this fiercely beautiful woman. I’ve learned from her in all directions and I’m just so glad that our souls found each other...❤️❤️ Thank you @gap for this photo for your holiday campaign it’s still a favorite!!

node.text:
This is 5. Birthday, bed head, balloons...perfection.
Jo, I love you to the moon and back million times a trillion times and then some.
